<L>__{exterior nix's house late afternoon}
<A>__{a car comes to a halt outside the house, where six vehicles are already gathered. the snake handling cultist gets out. snakes seethe out of the open car door.}
<L>__{interior nix's house various late afternoon}
<A>__{we move through the shadowy interior, catching sight of several cultists as we go. they all have looks of barely suppressed ecstasy on their faces. we are moving towards the sanctum, and it's getting darker. a match is struck, and an oil flame sputters into life. we see norman's gleaming face. on the wall is a picture of nix, floating over a scene of apocalyptic destruction. norman brushes away thirteen years' accrual of dirt. beneath, nix's expression is as rabid and terrifying as ever. norman grins.}
